  _eventName: A points-based cycling license to regulate urban cycling
  _date: September 26, 2024
  _subheading: ' To improve safety, France introduced a points-based cycling license
    for public road use, aiming to raise cyclist responsibility and better regulate
    this growing transport mode.'
  _coverImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 63e7cdb0f96db1612b9b3ce7e5ed8081, type: 3}
